00:00:59.537 --> 00:01:07.787
In 2016 Forbes Magazine published an article titled “The Rise of the Freelancer Economy”.

00:01:08.617 --> 00:01:14.567
In it, the author wrote, and I’m quoting directly, “Who says you can’t drive an Uber in

